    <summary>Estilo ABNT adaptado para as normas da UNIARP, com base na NBR 10520:2023 e NBR 6023:2018. Baseado em um CSL ABNT mais antigo.</summary> <updated>2025-05-07T22:30:00-03:00</updated> <rights license="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/3.0/">This work is licensed under a Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 3.0 License</rights>
